---
<section id="personal" class="relative py-24 px-6 bg-soft-bg overflow-hidden border-t border-charcoal/5">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center">
    
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-joy-yellow font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-4">
        Explorer & Adventurer
      </h2>
      <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-charcoal mb-6 font-outfit">
        Osobní Radost
      </h3>
      <p class="text-lg text-charcoal/60 max-w-xl mx-auto font-medium">
        Chasing peaks, riding trails, and crafting memories. Osobní zodpovědnost za vlastní radost v akci.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Photo Grid Placeholder -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 w-full mb-20">
      {[1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6].map((i) => (
        <div class="aspect-[4/3] bg-charcoal/5 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-300 relative group">
           <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-joy-yellow/10 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"></div>
           <div class="w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center text-charcoal/10 font-bold italic">MTB / Mountains {i}</div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- YouTube / Instagram Highlights -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 w-full mb-12">
      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@michaltrs" target="_blank" class="p-8 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-charcoal/5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all group">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-red-600 mb-6 group-hover:bg-red-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2.5 17a24.12 24.12 0 0 1 0-10 2 2 0 0 1 2-2h15a2 2 0 0 1 2 2 24.12 24.12 0 0 1 0 10 2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-15a2 2 0 0 1-2-2Z"/><path d="m10 15 5-3-5-3v6Z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">YouTube Dokumenty</h4>
        <p class="text-charcoal/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Moje video-deníky z MTB expedic, skialpových výprav a outdoorových dobrodružství.
        </p>
        <span class="font-bold text-red-600">Sledovat na YouTube →</span>
      </a>

      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/michal_trs/" target="_blank" class="p-8 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-charcoal/5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all group">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-pink-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-pink-600 mb-6 group-hover:bg-pink-600 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="20" height="20" x="2" y="2" rx="5" ry="5"/><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"/><line x1="17.5" x2="17.51" y1="6.5" y2="6.5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Instagram Reel</h4>
        <p class="text-charcoal/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Každodenní radosti, momentky z cest a střípky z MTB tras v reálném čase.
        </p>
        <span class="font-bold text-pink-600">Sledovat na Instagramu →</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Community & Passions -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 w-full">
      <div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-charcoal/5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-joy-yellow/20 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-charcoal mb-6">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Němý Medvěd Brewery</h4>
        <p class="text-charcoal/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Co-founder & Head Brewer. Crafting small-batch, adventurous beers in the heart of the mountains. Joy in every sip.
        </p>
        <a href="https://www.brlohmelnik.cz/pivovar/" target="_blank" class="font-bold text-joy-yellow hover:underline flex items-center gap-2">
          Pivovar →
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-charcoal/5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-orange-600 mb-6">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 10c0 1-1 2-3 2h-1a1 1 0 0 1-1-1v-1a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h1c2 0 3-1 3-2a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2c0 1 1 2 3 2h1a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-1c-2 0-3 1-3 2a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h3a2 2 0 0 0 2-2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Movember</h4>
        <p class="text-charcoal/60 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Část komunity Mo Genovators. Podcast interview o mužském zdraví a možnost podpořit dobrou věc.
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <a href="https://soundcloud.com/mu-i-proti-rakovin/muzi-proti-rakovine-podcast-s-michalem-trsem" target="_blank" class="font-bold text-orange-600 hover:underline flex items-center gap-2">
            Podcast →
          </a>
          <a href="https://movember.com/m/michaltrs?mc=1" target="_blank" class="font-bold text-orange-600 hover:underline flex items-center gap-2">
            Přispět →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>


  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .font-outfit { font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; }
</style>
